ğŸ‘‰ Used in bit masking
3ï¸âƒ£ XOR (^) â­ IMPORTANT

ğŸ‘‰ Same â†’ 0
ğŸ‘‰ Different â†’ 1

1 ^ 1 = 0
1 ^ 0 = 1


Example:

